wikipedia_page.main: Joanne Elizabeth Calvino (born (1980-08-18)18 August 1980) is a British female weightlifter, competing in the 48 kg category and representing England or Great Britain at international competitions. She competed at world championships, most recently at the 2011 World Weightlifting Championships.
